    "body": "Fixes #3415\r\nFixes #1411\r\n\r\n**Issue**\r\n- The code was using the deprecated `isDrawingCacheEnabled` and `drawingCache` methods of the View class, which caused issues with newer Gradle versions.\r\n- When opening a tab in the background (as configured in the settings), the tab's thumbnail always appeared as black because the tab had never been opened.\r\n\r\n**Fix**\r\n- Refactored the tab preview functionality to utilize WebView instead of creating bitmaps.\r\n  - This change improves performance and memory usage by eliminating the need to create and store bitmaps for tab previews.\r\n  - To disable WebView controls when the tabs are visible, a temporary view was created and placed on top of the WebView, covering it completely to prevent WebView click events.\r\n  - Adjusted the height of the WebView when showing and hiding tabs to account for the default top margin imposed by the presence of a toolbar.\r\n\r\n- Removed the deprecated `ImageUtils.kt` class, which was no longer needed.\r\n\r\n**Additional Changes**\r\n- Added necessary comments to improve code understanding and provide context for the modifications.\r\n\r\n**Kiwix App**\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/kiwix/kiwix-android/assets/34593983/f75a4a59-3b31-4ae7-b77a-59345b1b06b6\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n**Custom App**\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/kiwix/kiwix-android/assets/34593983/53e36408-6832-4c9b-bfe3-b1f167ac38b9\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
